# Optional: where Vite proxies `/api` in dev (default reads PORT from ../backend/.env → http://127.0.0.1:PORT)
# VITE_PROXY_API=http://127.0.0.1:5000
#
# Do NOT set VITE_API_BASE while using `npm run dev` — it is ignored on purpose so `/api` always uses the proxy.
# Set VITE_API_BASE only for production builds / static hosting (e.g. http://localhost:5000).
#
# Payment modal: in production builds, set to "true" to complete checkout UI even when /payments/mock fails (demo only).
# In `npm run dev`, lenient mode is already on so mock payments can complete without a working DB.
# VITE_PAYMENT_TEST_ALWAYS_OK=true
